                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>belong thereto. But all this occurred before I came to\n                                                  <placeName>Canada</placeName> as I before<lb/>\n                                        said—else I would have acted as mediator—now it is a\n                                        different<lb/> matter to bring things around. If it had been\n                                        a <add>?</add>, the Cong had<lb/> determined to make him pay\n                                        handsomely—even his relations. As it<lb/> is don't be\n                                        surprised if you have to name the young one in the<lb/>\n                                        <add>?</add>—of course all I have said of this affair is\n                                                  sub<add>?</add><lb/> My dear fellow, you appear\n                                        just as anxious as you would represent<lb/> me to appear, to\n                                        demonstrate that you have no claims on<lb/> the ladies we\n                                        have discovered about. Claims? Who said you had?<lb/> Have\n                                        you any <hi rend=\"underline\">old Orients</hi> &amp;tc which\n                                        you could let me have, as their<lb/> perusal would be some\n                                        benefit to me in rubbing up what little I know<lb/> of\n                                        Deutsch. You would oblige me much by lending them me as\n                                        you<lb/> receive them, you might send them by opportunity\n                                        and so I would<lb/> return them. My father receives them\n                                        all, but it would be difficult<lb/> and expensive to receive\n                                        them from <placeName>Europe</placeName>.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I trust that having written you so frequently\n                                        lately that<lb/> you will not be quite so cheery with your\n                                        correspondence but let<lb/> me hear from you soon and fully.\n                                        One half the topics I write you<lb/> on you never deign to\n                                        answer <add>?</add> I insert you an invitation<lb/> to come\n                                        in here in the summer.—<add>ואין קול</add>! Wait till I ask\n                                        you<lb/> again. I asked you, “are you going to publish\n                                                  Peril<add>?</add>\n                                        <add>ואין עונה</add>! You<lb/> are certainly a civil\n                                        gentleman to say the least of you, still I conclude\n                                        nevertheless<lb/> with health and prosperity to you, wishing\n                                        you may enjoy every,<lb/> happiness that I wish</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(7)\">Yours very sincerely</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(8)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">Abraham de Sola</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                                        <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p><persName>Miss Catherine Vallentine</persName> died <date>Wed, 17\n                                                  Jany</date></p>\n                              <p> she was sister to <persName>Mr Valentine</persName> One of</p>\n                              <p>the founders of the Syn. Does she deserve</p>\n                              <p>an obituary in the Oc. or are these paid for—</p>\n                              <p> She was a truly, religious and charitable person.</p>\n                              <p><persName>Jacob</persName> send you some of my article till</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I hear from you.</p>\n                    </body>\n          </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
